{
  "texts": [
    "Because the models are highly complex, encompassing tens of billions of parameters, they cannot provide-and we cannot ascertain-the rationale for their output.",
    "And because they are trained on vast swaths of online data, they can be manipulated to produce harmful effects.",
    "Although many factors may shape the use of LLMs in health care, 1 in this Viewpoint, we focus on three key areas: accuracy, explainability, and security.",
    "When AI is used to target advertisements to online shoppers, errors have limited consequences.",
    "But in high-stakes fields such as health care, high levels of accuracy are needed."
  ]
}